content:
Develop interactive user interfaces so that your users can view and change data in OmniStudio for Vlocity.

Vlocity Lightning Web Components: Use standard JavaScript and HTML to modify and extend Vlocity products with a declarative 'clicks not code' approach.

OmniScripts: Craft dynamic customer interactions without code, deployable to multiple channels and devices. Define once, deploy within Salesforce or on a web page.

Vlocity Cards Framework: Build customer-centric, industry-specific UI components and applications using tools provided by the Vlocity Cards Framework.

OmniOut: Run LWC OmniScripts and FlexCards off-platform on third-party websites with OmniOut for OmniScripts and OmniOut for FlexCards. Display and connect to Salesforce from a CMS's external website.

Vlocity Actions: Automatically generated URLs that launch OmniScripts, Cards components, web pages, or external applications, specific to a given object type.

Vlocity Conversation UI: Combines online chat with transactional capabilities of Vlocityâ€™s Industry Cloud solutions.

OmniForm: An omnichannel tool for building single-step, dynamic customer interactions.

Vlocity OmniAnalytics Overview: Track user interactions and answer questions about advertisements, purchasing processes, and more. Can track interactions with or without a third-party system like Google Analytics.
title: Vlocity User Interaction Tools
